1
00:01:30,260 --> 00:01:34,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font size="12"><font color="#f5f5f5">Episode <font size="19">9</font></font></font></font></font>

2
00:01:30,260 --> 00:01:34,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font size="12"><font color="#f5f5f5">Episode <font size="19">9</font></font></font></font></font>

3
00:01:30,260 --> 00:01:34,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font size="10"><font color="#effefb">The Misanthrope and the Heart's Deepest Desire</font></font></font></font>

4
00:01:30,260 --> 00:01:34,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font size="10"><font color="#effefb">The Misanthrope and the Heart's Deepest Desire</font></font></font></font>

5
00:01:32,500 --> 00:01:34,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<b><font color="#656c6f"><font size="22">Director's Office</font></font></b></font>

6
00:01:34,660 --> 00:01:36,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}What do you think of the advanced class?</font>

7
00:01:37,140 --> 00:01:38,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It hasn't been without its trouble,</font>

8
00:01:39,090 --> 00:01:42,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but things have settled down 
since Ohgami decided on her career path.</font>

9
00:01:42,630 --> 00:01:43,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's good.</font>

10
00:01:44,230 --> 00:01:46,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now it's your turn, Haneda.</font>

11
00:01:47,020 --> 00:01:48,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Me?</font>

12
00:01:48,670 --> 00:01:49,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

13
00:01:49,790 --> 00:01:52,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you want to do 
after you become human?</font>

14
00:01:52,740 --> 00:01:55,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Make music, I suppose.</font>

15
00:01:55,090 --> 00:01:56,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really?</font>

16
00:01:56,570 --> 00:01:58,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd say I'm about half-serious.</font>

17
00:01:58,850 --> 00:02:01,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And the other half?</font>

18
00:02:01,650 --> 00:02:04,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to live life 
like you do, Mr. Hitoma.</font>

19
00:02:04,950 --> 00:02:06,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you messing with me?</font>

20
00:02:06,860 --> 00:02:10,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've got plenty 
to enjoy in life, don't you?</font>

21
00:02:10,570 --> 00:02:12,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Indulging your passions into the night.</font>

22
00:02:12,600 --> 00:02:15,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't say it like that! 
I'm just going to play video games!</font>

23
00:02:16,470 --> 00:02:20,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to create things 
that I love, just like you do.</font>

24
00:02:21,580 --> 00:02:25,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There may be setbacks, 
but I know they'll help me grow kinder.</font>

25
00:02:26,760 --> 00:02:28,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just like you, Mr. Hitoma.</font>

26
00:02:29,310 --> 00:02:31,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wouldn't call myself very kind.</font>

27
00:02:32,250 --> 00:02:33,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure you are.</font>

28
00:02:34,070 --> 00:02:37,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In my eyes, you come off as very human.</font>

29
00:02:38,060 --> 00:02:40,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What does "human" even mean here?</font>

30
00:02:41,460 --> 00:02:43,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How you're not perfect.</font>

31
00:02:43,440 --> 00:02:46,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mr. Hitoma, have you ever gotten angry?</font>

32
00:02:46,100 --> 00:02:47,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

33
00:02:47,070 --> 00:02:48,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Any bad memories?</font>

34
00:02:48,710 --> 00:02:50,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Plenty of them.</font>

35
00:02:50,430 --> 00:02:52,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What about happy ones?</font>

36
00:02:52,080 --> 00:02:53,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Plenty of those, too.</font>

37
00:02:53,760 --> 00:02:55,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Painful memories?</font>

38
00:02:55,440 --> 00:02:56,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lots of them.</font>

39
00:02:56,710 --> 00:02:58,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Times you've given up?</font>

40
00:02:58,630 --> 00:03:00,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I give up on something every day.</font>

41
00:03:01,310 --> 00:03:03,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Times you've been sad?</font>

42
00:03:03,900 --> 00:03:05,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">More than I can remember.</font>

43
00:03:06,070 --> 00:03:10,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There are all sorts of emotions 
that have brought color to your life.</font>

44
00:03:11,210 --> 00:03:14,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All of them are what 
make you who you are now.</font>

45
00:03:16,310 --> 00:03:18,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have plenty of things I regret, too.</font>

46
00:03:21,010 --> 00:03:22,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Say, Mr. Hitoma.</font>

47
00:03:22,190 --> 00:03:23,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is it?</font>

48
00:03:23,390 --> 00:03:27,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you could face your regrets, 
would you give them your best?</font>

49
00:03:27,820 --> 00:03:28,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's that mean?</font>

50
00:03:28,810 --> 00:03:30,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just a hypothetical.</font>

51
00:03:30,590 --> 00:03:33,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Would you rather forget your regrets?</font>

52
00:03:33,210 --> 00:03:34,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Or face them head-on?</font>

53
00:03:36,510 --> 00:03:37,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well...</font>

54
00:03:38,390 --> 00:03:41,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I could do everything over...</font>

55
00:03:42,770 --> 00:03:45,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd want to face them... I think.</font>

56
00:03:46,610 --> 00:03:47,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

57
00:03:47,930 --> 00:03:50,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mr. Hitoma, you've grown stronger.</font>

58
00:03:51,690 --> 00:03:53,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It'd be nice if that was the case.</font>

59
00:03:55,250 --> 00:03:58,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's time once again 
for the advanced class final assignments.</font>

60
00:03:59,300 --> 00:04:03,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To graduate and become human, 
you'll have to pass your final assignment.</font>

61
00:04:04,210 --> 00:04:06,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everyone gets a different assignment.</font>

62
00:04:06,630 --> 00:04:08,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please give it your all.</font>

63
00:04:09,590 --> 00:04:13,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How come I'm the only 
one who got this big box?!</font>

64
00:04:13,910 --> 00:04:15,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is that?</font>

65
00:04:17,160 --> 00:04:19,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My final assignment.</font>

66
00:04:19,430 --> 00:04:21,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's shattered into pieces.</font>

67
00:04:21,810 --> 00:04:25,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Machi broke it because 
she's rash and reckless.</font>

68
00:04:26,270 --> 00:04:28,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's already failed her assignment.</font>

69
00:04:28,630 --> 00:04:30,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nuh-uh!</font>

70
00:04:30,320 --> 00:04:33,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My assignment is 
to repair this with kintsugi!</font>

71
00:04:34,020 --> 00:04:37,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, they have assignments like that?</font>

72
00:04:38,180 --> 00:04:40,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What about you, Uchami?</font>

73
00:04:40,920 --> 00:04:44,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have to write letters 
to everyone in the advanced class.</font>

74
00:04:44,780 --> 00:04:47,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? That's a piece of cake!</font>

75
00:04:47,010 --> 00:04:49,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'll be done writing that in no time!</font>

76
00:04:49,770 --> 00:04:50,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not fair!</font>

77
00:04:51,310 --> 00:04:52,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Be a little more serious.</font>

78
00:04:52,810 --> 00:04:55,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even if I write down whatever, 
it won't be graded well.</font>

79
00:04:55,420 --> 00:04:57,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Guess you're right.</font>

80
00:04:58,230 --> 00:05:01,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">On top of the final assignment, 
I need to study to get into med school.</font>

81
00:05:02,390 --> 00:05:04,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have so much on my plate.</font>

82
00:05:04,000 --> 00:05:07,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You even have Mr. Hoshino 
helping you study after school.</font>

83
00:05:08,610 --> 00:05:10,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's the assignment for you two, Ohgami?</font>

84
00:05:11,490 --> 00:05:13,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A-As for me...</font>

85
00:05:14,350 --> 00:05:20,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I need to write reviews for ten works, 
which include novels, comics, and essays.</font>

86
00:05:20,620 --> 00:05:22,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ten of them?!</font>

87
00:05:22,550 --> 00:05:28,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The Tale of Genji,</i> Kafka's <i>Metamorphosis,</i> 
and much more, even American comic books.</font>

88
00:05:29,990 --> 00:05:32,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What'd you get as an assignment, Ryuzaki?</font>

89
00:05:32,650 --> 00:05:37,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have to take on the dorm 
mother Ryouko's work for ten days.</font>

90
00:05:37,440 --> 00:05:39,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really? That sounds rough.</font>

91
00:05:39,930 --> 00:05:43,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I hear Ryouko will be away for ten days.</font>

92
00:05:43,160 --> 00:05:44,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll be taking over during that time.</font>

93
00:05:45,510 --> 00:05:48,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So you have to cook for the dorms?</font>

94
00:05:48,690 --> 00:05:50,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's more to it than that.</font>

95
00:05:50,510 --> 00:05:52,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She also looks after the beginner class,</font>

96
00:05:52,710 --> 00:05:56,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">not to mention cleaning, laundry, 
all sorts of small tasks...</font>

97
00:05:56,160 --> 00:05:59,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And dealing with whatever 
problems pop up, too.</font>

98
00:05:59,130 --> 00:06:01,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sounds like a heavy workload.</font>

99
00:06:02,070 --> 00:06:04,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wonder if I'll be able to handle it.</font>

100
00:06:04,970 --> 00:06:08,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'll do just fine, Karin. Good luck.</font>

101
00:06:08,330 --> 00:06:10,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you, Tobari!</font>

102
00:06:10,660 --> 00:06:15,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll think of it as practice 
for when I marry Mr. Rei!</font>

103
00:06:15,200 --> 00:06:16,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">S-Sure...</font>

104
00:06:17,330 --> 00:06:20,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's your assignment, Tobari?</font>

105
00:06:20,180 --> 00:06:23,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have to make a musical 
instrument by hand.</font>

106
00:06:23,790 --> 00:06:25,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A musical instrument by hand?</font>

107
00:06:25,550 --> 00:06:26,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you going to make?</font>

108
00:06:27,540 --> 00:06:29,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's a good question.</font>

109
00:06:29,300 --> 00:06:31,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You haven't decided yet?</font>

110
00:06:31,460 --> 00:06:34,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nope, but I think it'll be fun.</font>

111
00:06:37,380 --> 00:06:40,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's looking pretty big. 
What are you making?</font>

112
00:06:40,660 --> 00:06:45,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">An electric guitar. 
I was thinking of making it a Les Paul.</font>

113
00:06:46,350 --> 00:06:50,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can one person even make 
an electric guitar?</font>

114
00:06:50,650 --> 00:06:53,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They sell guitar necks 
with the frets and all,</font>

115
00:06:53,720 --> 00:06:57,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">as well as parts like pegs, 
bridges, and all the circuitry.</font>

116
00:06:57,860 --> 00:07:00,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see. It's totally beyond me!</font>

117
00:07:01,330 --> 00:07:03,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This sure is a squeaking pain.</font>

118
00:07:03,540 --> 00:07:06,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Traditional craft? More like a puzzle!</font>

119
00:07:06,360 --> 00:07:08,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shut up, Machi!</font>

120
00:07:08,480 --> 00:07:13,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Squeak! Tobari's woodworking's 
way louder than me!</font>

121
00:07:13,570 --> 00:07:16,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's part of her assignment, 
so I don't mind it.</font>

122
00:07:16,930 --> 00:07:19,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey! Stop playing favorites!</font>

123
00:07:21,190 --> 00:07:23,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Looks like Ohgami's busy reading.</font>

124
00:07:24,610 --> 00:07:26,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's that you're reading, Ryuzaki?</font>

125
00:07:27,130 --> 00:07:29,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A manual for performing 
dorm mother duties.</font>

126
00:07:30,130 --> 00:07:33,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ryouko wrote down all the important parts.</font>

127
00:07:34,210 --> 00:07:37,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ryouko's as reliable as ever, I see.</font>

128
00:07:37,310 --> 00:07:49,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font size="15"><font face="Times New Roman"><b><font color="#c92b4c">Shiranui High
Student Dorm Manual</font></b></font></font></font>

129
00:07:37,650 --> 00:07:41,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She even wrote down tips for dealing 
with all of the beginner class students.</font>

130
00:07:42,620 --> 00:07:46,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All the students at this school 
are way too quirky!</font>

131
00:07:46,020 --> 00:07:48,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're pretty quirky yourself, Ryuzaki.</font>

132
00:07:52,530 --> 00:07:56,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your guitar's really starting 
to take shape after a week.</font>

133
00:07:56,420 --> 00:07:59,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mr. Hitoma, listen to this!</font>

134
00:07:59,050 --> 00:08:00,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Karin's such a meanie!</font>

135
00:08:00,740 --> 00:08:02,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Give her a good lecture!</font>

136
00:08:02,520 --> 00:08:07,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Machi. Crying 
to Mr. Rei is playing dirty.</font>

137
00:08:07,560 --> 00:08:08,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What happened?</font>

138
00:08:08,890 --> 00:08:11,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She won't let me have seconds when I eat!</font>

139
00:08:11,890 --> 00:08:12,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

140
00:08:12,710 --> 00:08:15,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The budget doesn't allow for it.</font>

141
00:08:15,280 --> 00:08:17,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't go against the rules.</font>

142
00:08:17,790 --> 00:08:21,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Isn't it your job 
to make all of that work out?</font>

143
00:08:21,380 --> 00:08:23,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're a no-good crooked magistrate!</font>

144
00:08:24,400 --> 00:08:27,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shut up already!</font>

145
00:08:27,580 --> 00:08:28,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Usami?</font>

146
00:08:29,750 --> 00:08:32,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I'm sorry.</font>

147
00:08:35,460 --> 00:08:37,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't mind me.</font>

148
00:08:37,430 --> 00:08:39,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You just took me by surprise...</font>

149
00:08:43,000 --> 00:08:44,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's my fault.</font>

150
00:08:47,690 --> 00:08:48,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Usami!</font>

151
00:08:49,340 --> 00:08:50,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry, Haneda.</font>

152
00:08:50,380 --> 00:08:52,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wrap up the rest of class for me.</font>

153
00:08:52,400 --> 00:08:53,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Got it!</font>

154
00:08:57,910 --> 00:08:59,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mr. Hitoma.</font>

155
00:09:01,480 --> 00:09:03,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ms. Karasuma.</font>

156
00:09:03,600 --> 00:09:06,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Usami's in the nurse's office.</font>

157
00:09:10,750 --> 00:09:11,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Usami.</font>

158
00:09:12,570 --> 00:09:14,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm awful.</font>

159
00:09:15,560 --> 00:09:16,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I get annoyed easily.</font>

160
00:09:17,540 --> 00:09:19,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have angry outbursts.</font>

161
00:09:20,130 --> 00:09:22,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I made Isaki cry...</font>

162
00:09:24,440 --> 00:09:31,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry. I was the one making 
the most trouble in class.</font>

163
00:09:32,540 --> 00:09:34,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's fine.</font>

164
00:09:34,700 --> 00:09:36,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's fine about that?</font>

165
00:09:37,080 --> 00:09:42,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everyone has times when dealing 
with others gets to be too much.</font>

166
00:09:42,860 --> 00:09:43,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know that.</font>

167
00:09:44,890 --> 00:09:46,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's right.</font>

168
00:09:47,470 --> 00:09:51,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'll feel calmer 
after a nice, warm drink.</font>

169
00:09:53,590 --> 00:09:54,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's good.</font>

170
00:09:55,800 --> 00:09:57,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Glad to hear it.</font>

171
00:09:58,780 --> 00:10:02,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll apologize when I go back 
to the classroom.</font>

172
00:10:02,550 --> 00:10:03,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

173
00:10:03,670 --> 00:10:06,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry I didn't warn them 
about being too loud.</font>

174
00:10:07,130 --> 00:10:09,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, you should be.</font>

175
00:10:10,050 --> 00:10:12,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Looks like you're feeling a bit better.</font>

176
00:10:12,550 --> 00:10:13,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Usami.</font>

177
00:10:13,910 --> 00:10:16,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks for putting 
the nurse's office to good use.</font>

178
00:10:17,370 --> 00:10:21,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm always here, so feel free 
to drop by whenever you need.</font>

179
00:10:22,580 --> 00:10:26,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Haruka, why'd you decide 
to become a school nurse?</font>

180
00:10:27,640 --> 00:10:32,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wanted to give people 
a place to run away to.</font>

181
00:10:33,370 --> 00:10:35,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A place to run away to?</font>

182
00:10:35,900 --> 00:10:39,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You get people like that, 
who work a little too hard.</font>

183
00:10:41,420 --> 00:10:43,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't look at me like that.</font>

184
00:10:45,010 --> 00:10:49,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's always better to have 
more places you can turn to.</font>

185
00:10:50,020 --> 00:10:52,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<b><font color="#7b8184"><font size="30">Advanced Class</font></font></b></font>

186
00:10:59,940 --> 00:11:03,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? Stop staring at me.</font>

187
00:11:03,330 --> 00:11:08,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see you're working on your 
assignment instead of studying.</font>

188
00:11:08,520 --> 00:11:09,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Making good progress?</font>

189
00:11:10,450 --> 00:11:12,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not cut out 
for this kind of assignment.</font>

190
00:11:13,500 --> 00:11:16,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It should have been 
a writer like Isaki who does this.</font>

191
00:11:17,820 --> 00:11:22,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Isn't the point of the assignment 
for you to get over not being good at it?</font>

192
00:11:23,560 --> 00:11:25,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know that already.</font>

193
00:11:25,240 --> 00:11:27,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was complaining, 
not asking for an explanation.</font>

194
00:11:28,520 --> 00:11:29,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How about you, Machi?</font>

195
00:11:30,230 --> 00:11:32,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm glad you asked.</font>

196
00:11:32,770 --> 00:11:38,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Believe it or not, today will be the final
step for my dear Bowledoodle!</font>

197
00:11:38,830 --> 00:11:41,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Bowl-a-what now?</font>

198
00:11:41,640 --> 00:11:43,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bowledoodle!</font>

199
00:11:43,090 --> 00:11:46,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The name of the bowl 
I've been looking after!</font>

200
00:11:50,760 --> 00:11:53,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Looks like Ohgami's struggling.</i></font>

201
00:11:57,930 --> 00:11:59,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There we go!</font>

202
00:11:59,500 --> 00:12:00,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think I'm all done!</font>

203
00:12:00,920 --> 00:12:03,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You really made a guitar?</font>

204
00:12:03,730 --> 00:12:05,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The wood grain looks so cool.</font>

205
00:12:06,200 --> 00:12:09,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is my first time seeing 
an electric guitar in person!</font>

206
00:12:28,020 --> 00:12:30,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You play that thing really well, Haneda.</font>

207
00:12:31,860 --> 00:12:32,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really?</font>

208
00:12:33,910 --> 00:12:35,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks, Mr. Hitoma.</font>

209
00:12:35,910 --> 00:12:38,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm off to go submit it to the principal!</font>

210
00:12:41,110 --> 00:12:43,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's so cool that she can play 
an instrument.</font>

211
00:12:44,180 --> 00:12:48,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mr. Rei, do you like girls 
who can play instruments?</font>

212
00:12:48,260 --> 00:12:53,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, it's more that I respect 
people who are multi-talented.</font>

213
00:12:53,020 --> 00:12:55,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see. I learned something new!</font>

214
00:12:55,710 --> 00:12:58,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks, Mr. Rei! I love you!</font>

215
00:13:00,500 --> 00:13:02,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Again with the immoral displays.</font>

216
00:13:02,550 --> 00:13:04,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're working hard, too, Usami.</font>

217
00:13:04,780 --> 00:13:06,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll do it since I've been asked to.</font>

218
00:13:07,390 --> 00:13:11,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But Isaki must be a real masochist 
to do this every day.</font>

219
00:13:11,210 --> 00:13:12,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-What?!</font>

220
00:13:16,230 --> 00:13:18,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">E-Excuse us.</font>

221
00:13:19,130 --> 00:13:23,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh? You're from the beginner class.</font>

222
00:13:24,470 --> 00:13:27,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Karin! Thanks for everything 
over the past ten days!</font>

223
00:13:28,360 --> 00:13:30,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you!</font>

224
00:13:30,980 --> 00:13:33,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Th-Thanks...</font>

225
00:13:36,660 --> 00:13:39,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh! Those are so cute!</font>

226
00:13:39,730 --> 00:13:45,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They asked me to teach them 
how to make icing.</font>

227
00:13:46,070 --> 00:13:49,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So this is what they were trying to make.</font>

228
00:13:50,730 --> 00:13:56,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't get to see it, but looks 
like you did just fine as dorm mother.</font>

229
00:13:56,500 --> 00:13:58,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, of course.</font>

230
00:14:00,840 --> 00:14:03,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nezu, how's your assignment going?</font>

231
00:14:03,600 --> 00:14:06,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Squeak! I-I'll submit it sooner or later.</font>

232
00:14:06,570 --> 00:14:10,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Didn't you say you were 
on the last step yesterday?</font>

233
00:14:11,270 --> 00:14:13,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How come you remember that?</font>

234
00:14:13,270 --> 00:14:14,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't click your tongue at me!</font>

235
00:14:14,870 --> 00:14:21,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But once I submit it, 
Bowledoodle's gonna be gone!</font>

236
00:14:21,770 --> 00:14:25,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? You usually get to 
keep it afterwards.</font>

237
00:14:25,970 --> 00:14:28,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, really?</font>

238
00:14:28,160 --> 00:14:31,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. I got to keep this guitar.</font>

239
00:14:31,370 --> 00:14:34,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well now I feel stupid 
for worrying so much.</font>

240
00:14:37,350 --> 00:14:39,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How's it going, Ohgami?</font>

241
00:14:39,150 --> 00:14:43,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">W-Well, I do have a good 
deal of it sorted out...</font>

242
00:14:44,070 --> 00:14:45,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's up?</font>

243
00:14:45,470 --> 00:14:48,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wonder if these reviews are good enough.</font>

244
00:14:49,400 --> 00:14:53,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't help but worry that 
I may have misinterpreted something.</font>

245
00:14:54,900 --> 00:14:57,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everyone gets something 
different out of art.</font>

246
00:14:57,770 --> 00:15:00,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You should write down exactly 
how you feel about them.</font>

247
00:15:01,110 --> 00:15:03,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, but still...</font>

248
00:15:08,510 --> 00:15:10,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Isaki's report is straight-up fire!</font>

249
00:15:10,810 --> 00:15:13,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's so good at tying it all together!</font>

250
00:15:13,030 --> 00:15:14,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Isaki.</font>

251
00:15:15,030 --> 00:15:17,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Help me with my assignment.</font>

252
00:15:17,370 --> 00:15:19,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? You don't mean Isaki?</font>

253
00:15:20,470 --> 00:15:24,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My assignment is to write a letter 
for everyone in the advanced class.</font>

254
00:15:25,210 --> 00:15:28,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You mean I'm included in that?</font>

255
00:15:29,020 --> 00:15:30,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course you are.</font>

256
00:15:30,660 --> 00:15:34,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I miss my chance today, I have to 
wait a month, which will be too late.</font>

257
00:15:34,580 --> 00:15:36,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So I wrote yours first.</font>

258
00:15:39,390 --> 00:15:41,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ushami!</font>

259
00:15:41,080 --> 00:15:44,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">H-Hey! Get your grubby mitts off me!</font>

260
00:15:44,010 --> 00:15:45,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Isaki, sit!</font>

261
00:15:47,690 --> 00:15:49,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No hesitation!</font>

262
00:15:49,560 --> 00:15:54,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just keep in mind that I'm not 
as good at writing as Isaki.</font>

263
00:15:54,270 --> 00:15:57,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Writing letters isn't about 
how good or bad you are!</font>

264
00:15:57,230 --> 00:15:58,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so happy!</font>

265
00:15:58,850 --> 00:16:01,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, can I read it now? 
I don't think I can wait!</font>

266
00:16:02,610 --> 00:16:03,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">S-Sure...</font>

267
00:16:03,900 --> 00:16:07,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's yours now, so I can't stop you.</font>

268
00:16:07,530 --> 00:16:10,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sweet! Thanks!</font>

269
00:16:10,580 --> 00:16:12,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's see...</font>

270
00:16:21,560 --> 00:16:23,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks, Ushami...</font>

271
00:16:23,710 --> 00:16:29,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This stuff about my bright, cheery smile 
or how you think I'm considerate...</font>

272
00:16:29,090 --> 00:16:33,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I really appreciate all 
the good things you wrote about me!</font>

273
00:16:33,250 --> 00:16:37,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm <i>so</i> happy you feel that way, Ushami!</font>

274
00:16:35,820 --> 00:16:38,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I told you to get your hands off me!</font>

275
00:16:38,910 --> 00:16:42,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I <i>love</i> you lots too, Ushami!</font>

276
00:16:42,380 --> 00:16:46,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know we don't see each other often, 
but I'm glad you still remembered me!</font>

277
00:16:46,460 --> 00:16:47,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks, Ushami!</font>

278
00:16:47,970 --> 00:16:51,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How could I forget someone so annoying?</font>

279
00:16:51,840 --> 00:16:54,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? Guess I'll have to be more annoying!</font>

280
00:16:54,480 --> 00:16:55,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shut up!</font>

281
00:16:55,960 --> 00:16:59,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't wait for my letter from Usami.</font>

282
00:16:59,260 --> 00:17:02,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When will I be getting mine?</font>

283
00:17:02,830 --> 00:17:04,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm looking forward to it!</font>

284
00:17:05,700 --> 00:17:10,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Usami, you use simple words 
that directly convey how you feel.</font>

285
00:17:10,910 --> 00:17:13,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your writing is so thoughtful and sweet.</font>

286
00:17:13,360 --> 00:17:15,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I really love it.</font>

287
00:17:16,630 --> 00:17:19,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've never gotten a letter before.</font>

288
00:17:19,590 --> 00:17:22,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's like your words 
are coming alive on paper.</font>

289
00:17:22,650 --> 00:17:24,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How wonderful.</font>

290
00:17:25,450 --> 00:17:30,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can tell that you pay close attention 
to both me and yourself.</font>

291
00:17:30,000 --> 00:17:34,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've always admired 
how you never admit defeat.</font>

292
00:17:36,770 --> 00:17:38,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uchami...</font>

293
00:17:40,330 --> 00:17:42,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why'd you burst into tears?</font>

294
00:17:42,940 --> 00:17:46,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I never knew that's how you felt about me!</font>

295
00:17:46,670 --> 00:17:51,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Man, you really love me, don't you?!</font>

296
00:17:52,110 --> 00:17:55,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Machi, please don't cry.</font>

297
00:17:55,130 --> 00:17:57,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you start crying, I...</font>

298
00:17:58,870 --> 00:18:01,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I won't be able to stop myself, either!</font>

299
00:18:01,980 --> 00:18:05,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, don't you go crying now, Isaki.</font>

300
00:18:05,740 --> 00:18:08,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've been holding back this whole time!</font>

301
00:18:09,580 --> 00:18:12,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? Karin, too?</font>

302
00:18:12,010 --> 00:18:14,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hah! Usami made them cry!</font>

303
00:18:15,150 --> 00:18:17,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tobari! Don't make me 
sound like the bad guy!</font>

304
00:18:17,950 --> 00:18:21,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It really is all your fault, Usami...</font>

305
00:18:21,440 --> 00:18:26,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">After always being so stern, 
you're so kind in your letter...</font>

306
00:18:26,150 --> 00:18:28,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's right! What's the big idea?</font>

307
00:18:28,820 --> 00:18:30,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're head over heels for me!</font>

308
00:18:30,570 --> 00:18:33,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You didn't have to say all 
those nice things about me!</font>

309
00:18:34,580 --> 00:18:37,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cry or get angry, pick one!</font>

310
00:18:40,200 --> 00:18:43,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hitoma. This is my last letter.</font>

311
00:18:43,500 --> 00:18:45,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I get one, too?</font>

312
00:18:45,230 --> 00:18:48,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everyone in the advanced 
class includes you, Hitoma.</font>

313
00:18:49,330 --> 00:18:52,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not gonna fall 
for a simple trick question like that.</font>

314
00:18:54,030 --> 00:18:54,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Also...</font>

315
00:18:55,780 --> 00:18:59,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#544746">Neneko Kurosawa</font></font></font>

316
00:18:56,180 --> 00:18:58,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is for Neneko.</font>

317
00:18:59,850 --> 00:19:03,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She was a student this 
school year, so...</font>

318
00:19:04,270 --> 00:19:05,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks, Usami.</font>

319
00:19:06,120 --> 00:19:08,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll deliver this letter for you.</font>

320
00:19:08,770 --> 00:19:09,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks.</font>

321
00:19:09,930 --> 00:19:12,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not gonna read yours?</font>

322
00:19:12,090 --> 00:19:13,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll do it when I get home.</font>

323
00:19:13,860 --> 00:19:16,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? Why not now?</font>

324
00:19:16,780 --> 00:19:20,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nope. I bet I'll cry when I do.</font>

325
00:19:21,270 --> 00:19:22,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess that's true.</font>

326
00:19:22,680 --> 00:19:24,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've made up my mind.</font>

327
00:19:25,460 --> 00:19:28,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All this time, I've been worried 
about the reviews for my assignment.</font>

328
00:19:29,480 --> 00:19:32,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But thanks to Usami's letter, 
I've seen the light.</font>

329
00:19:33,530 --> 00:19:38,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Instead of stressing out over details, 
I need to plainly state the way I feel.</font>

330
00:19:38,680 --> 00:19:42,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's all I need to do in order 
to stir people's emotions.</font>

331
00:19:43,140 --> 00:19:45,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hurry up and finish 
your assignment, Isaki.</font>

332
00:19:45,810 --> 00:19:47,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know you can do it.</font>

333
00:19:48,090 --> 00:19:50,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes! Thank you!</font>

334
00:20:04,860 --> 00:20:07,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm done...</font>

335
00:20:07,710 --> 00:20:10,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good work! I know it must have been hard!</font>

336
00:20:10,730 --> 00:20:12,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you very much.</font>

337
00:20:12,750 --> 00:20:13,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nice going.</font>

338
00:20:13,870 --> 00:20:15,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good job.</font>

339
00:20:15,030 --> 00:20:17,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ichaki, you're amazing!</font>

340
00:20:17,890 --> 00:20:21,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Th-Thank you, everyone...</font>

341
00:20:23,180 --> 00:20:25,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ohgami, good work.</font>

342
00:20:25,740 --> 00:20:27,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You did your best.</font>

343
00:20:27,480 --> 00:20:28,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mr. Hitoma.</font>

344
00:20:29,370 --> 00:20:31,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you!</font>

345
00:20:31,400 --> 00:20:33,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Advanced class!</font>

346
00:20:33,940 --> 00:20:36,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A hearty congratulations to all of you!</font>

347
00:20:36,930 --> 00:20:38,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Principal.</font>

348
00:20:38,530 --> 00:20:44,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've just confirmed that you've all 
completed your graduation assignments.</font>

349
00:20:44,250 --> 00:20:50,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">After careful consideration, we've decided
who meets the graduation requirements!</font>

350
00:20:51,940 --> 00:20:54,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The students graduating this year...</font>

351
00:20:54,770 --> 00:20:56,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">are more diligent than the rest,</font>

352
00:20:56,470 --> 00:20:59,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">care greatly for others, 
and show deep passion for their interests.</font>

353
00:20:59,810 --> 00:21:06,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Faced with doubts and hardship, 
they persevered as a pair, hand-in-hand.</font>

354
00:21:06,830 --> 00:21:11,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cheerful and kind, 
they learned to love themselves.</font>

355
00:21:11,980 --> 00:21:14,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And for their graduation assignment,</font>

356
00:21:14,040 --> 00:21:18,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">from the words and ideas of tales old 
and new, from around the world,</font>

357
00:21:18,060 --> 00:21:20,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">they learned to communicate, 
or in other words,</font>

358
00:21:20,570 --> 00:21:26,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">express their thoughts and feelings 
with greater precision than before.</font>

359
00:21:29,750 --> 00:21:34,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For these reasons stated, 
this year's graduating students...</font>

360
00:21:35,100 --> 00:21:39,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Isaki Ohgami and Isaki Ohgami.</font>

361
00:21:39,540 --> 00:21:41,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It'll be you two.</font>

362
00:21:42,200 --> 00:21:46,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Once again, congratulations!</font>

363
00:21:49,000 --> 00:21:50,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you very much.</font>

364
00:21:58,380 --> 00:22:01,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you, everyone!</font>

365
